<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8272526>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–12. Adults of A. sinensis: 7. China, Tai-Shan, 19 mm, ♁11004; 8. China, Tai-Shan, 18.5 mm, ♁; 9. China, Tapaishan, 19.5 mm, ♀; 10. Afghanistan, Kotkai, 21.5 mm, ♁732.23; 11. yangtseella PLT, 18 mm, ♁622.21; 12. yangtseella PLT, 19.5 mm, ♀621.21." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8272526/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8272528>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–17. Head structures. 13–15. Male antennae. 16, 17. Heads of flavitinctella, lateral view: 16. Iran, Bandar-Abbas- Sirjan, ♁711.23; 17. India, Silent Valley, ♀636.22." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8272528/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8272530>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18–19. Male genitalia: a. ventral view, aedeagus is separated; b. editum of left valva, enlarged; c. editum of right valva, enlarged; d. aedeagus; e. culcita and tergum VIII. 18. flavitinctella, Iran, Bandar-Abbas-Sirjan, ♁711.23. 19. yangtseella PLT, ♁622.21. (Scale bars = 1mm. 18d—vesica is partially everted. 19d—vesica is everted)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8272530/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8272532>
    dc:description "FIGURES 20–22. Female genitalia: a. general (ventral) view; b. base of ductus seminalis, enlarged. 20. tchahabarella PLT, ♀600.21. 21. flavitinctella, India, Silent Valley, ♀635.22. 22. yangtseella PLT, ♀621.21." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8272532/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8272534>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23–30. Tympanal organs of Asclerobia spp.: 23–26. flavitinctella; 27–30. sinensis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8272534/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

